  "content/misc/assistant-architecture.csv": "step,title,icon,description\n1,Knowledge Base,fa-database,\"Resume, papers, posters, transcripts, project notes, and supporting files.\"\n2,Retrieval Layer,fa-magnifying-glass-chart,\"Documents are chunked, embedded, and searched through semantic retrieval.\"\n3,LLM Backend,fa-brain,\"A FastAPI backend retrieves relevant context and generates responses through an LLM.\"\n4,Web Interface,fa-window-maximize,\"The assistant is embedded directly into the portfolio with session memory and markdown rendering.\"\n",
