  "content/misc/research-references.csv": "order,name,image,relation,department,link\n1,Julia Mendelsohn,images/JuliaRef.webp,PI for my CLIP/CATS research assistant work,\"College of Information and Department of Government and Politics; UMIACS/CLIP Lab\",https://ischool.umd.edu/directory/julia-mendelsohn/\n2,Brian Kim,images/briankimRef.webp,Academic advisor and professor for SURV727 and SURV640,\"JPSM; Co-Director, Social Data Science Major\",https://jpsm.umd.edu/facultyprofile/kim/brian\n3,Raphael Nishimura,images/RaphaelRef.webp,Sampling I professor under whom I served as TA,\"Survey Research Operations, University of Michigan ISR\",https://src.isr.umich.edu/research/staff/profiles/nishimuraraphael/\n",
  "content/misc/research-selected.csv": "order,ref,label,interest\n1,ev,AAPOR 2025,\"Tests whether LLM-generated personas can be treated as public-opinion proxies by comparing them against Reddit and New York Times EV discourse.\"\n2,tda,NCSET 2024 Best Paper,\"Shows the mathematical side of my research identity: using Mapper and persistent homology to reason about structure in complex scientific data.\"\n",
  "content/misc/resume-copy.csv": "key,value\nheroEyebrow,Interactive Resume\nheroTitle,\"Research, survey methodology, and machine learning profile.\"\nheroLead,\"A structured, recruiter-readable version of my academic background, research experience, teaching, industry work, technical skills, and project outcomes across survey methodology, NLP, LLM systems, machine learning, and computational social science.\"\nquickSummaryLabel,Quick Summary\noverviewEyebrow,Welcome\noverviewTitle,Resume Overview\noverviewLead,\"Select a section above to open a full timeline or evidence grid. Each card can be expanded, and most entries are connected to SagnikGPT for recruiter-style follow-up questions.\"\nrecruiterEyebrow,30-second recruiter summary\nrecruiterTitle,\"Survey-trained data scientist with NLP, LLM, and research-system experience.\"\nrecruiterBody,\"I combine survey methodology, machine learning, NLP, and computational social science. My strongest work includes FrameScope, a live LLM-assisted AI discourse dashboard; ASHA survey response-rate analysis; EV sentiment analysis presented at AAPOR; GTI/media-framing research presented at IISA; and multistage sampling designs for applied survey problems.\"\noverviewAskLabel,Ask summary\noverviewAskPrompt,\"Summarize Sagnik's resume for a recruiter. Highlight education, research experience, skills, strongest projects, and measurable outcomes.\"\nrecruiterAskSummaryLabel,Ask SagnikGPT for recruiter summary ->\nrecruiterAskSummaryPrompt,\"Give a 30-second recruiter summary of Sagnik. Highlight his strongest evidence for data science, survey methodology, NLP, LLM systems, and research roles.\"\nrecruiterDataScientistLabel,Evaluate for data scientist ->\nrecruiterDataScientistPrompt,\"Evaluate Sagnik for a data scientist role. Be specific about strengths, project evidence, tools, and possible gaps.\"\nrecruiterSurveyRoleLabel,Evaluate for survey role ->\nrecruiterSurveyRolePrompt,\"Evaluate Sagnik for a survey methodologist or survey data scientist role. Use ASHA, Detroit sampling, Michigan sampling, coursework, and TA experience.\"\neducationEyebrow,Education Timeline\neducationTitle,Academic Background\neducationLead,\"Click an institution to open coursework. Click any course to ask SagnikGPT how that subject supports my profile.\"\neducationAskLabel,Ask academic trajectory\neducationAskPrompt,\"Explain Sagnik's academic trajectory from Statistics to Data Science to Survey and Data Science. Connect coursework to his research profile.\"\neducationBackLabel,<- Back to Education\neducationDetailEyebrow,Education Detail\nacademicFocusLabel,Academic focus:\ncourseworkTitle,Coursework\ncourseworkLead,Click a subject to ask SagnikGPT how it connects to my training and research profile.\ndegreeAskLabel,Ask about this degree ->\ndegreeAskPromptTemplate,\"How did Sagnik perform academically at {institution}? Explain how his coursework in {degree} supports his research and job profile.\"\ncourseAskPromptTemplate,\"How did Sagnik use or benefit from the course: {course} at {institution}? Connect it to his research, projects, and technical profile.\"\nexperienceEyebrow,Experience\nexperienceTitle,\"Research, Teaching, and Industry\"\nexperienceLead,\"Choose a category to open a timeline. Each entry expands into responsibilities, methods, metrics, and end results.\"\nexperienceAskLabel,Ask experience summary\nexperienceAskPrompt,\"Summarize Sagnik's experience across research, teaching, and industry. Highlight evidence and role fit.\"\nexperienceCategoryActionTemplate,Open {title} timeline ->\nexperienceTimelineEyebrow,Experience Timeline\nexperienceTimelineLead,\"Click any entry to view detailed responsibilities, methods, metrics, and SagnikGPT prompt.\"\nexperienceTimelineAskLabelTemplate,Ask about {heading} ->\nexperienceTimelineAskPromptTemplate,\"Summarize Sagnik's {heading}. Give specific evidence, methods, metrics, and role fit.\"\nexperienceBackLabel,<- Back to Experience\nexperienceBackShortLabel,<- Back\nexperienceDetailEyebrow,Experience Detail\nexperienceResultLabel,End result:\nexperienceAskRoleLabel,Ask SagnikGPT about this role\nsectionTitleResearch,Research Experience\nsectionTitleTeaching,Teaching Experience\nsectionTitleIndustry,Industry Experience\nsectionTitleDefault,Experience\nprojectsEyebrow,Projects Timeline\nprojectsTitle,\"Projects, Papers, Reports, and Posters\"\nprojectsLead,\"Click a project to open objective, abstract, motivation, methods, results, metrics, paper/report, poster, GitHub, and SagnikGPT prompt.\"\nprojectsAskLabel,Ask project fit\nprojectsAskPrompt,\"Which of Sagnik's projects are strongest for data science, NLP, survey methodology, and ML roles? Rank them using metrics and outcomes.\"\nprojectsBackLabel,<- Back to Projects\nprojectDetailEyebrow,Project Detail\nprojectObjectiveTitle,Objective\nprojectAbstractTitle,Abstract\nprojectMotivationTitle,Motivation\nprojectMethodsTitle,Methods\nprojectResultsTitle,End Results\nprojectInsightTitle,Research / Business Insight\nposterHelpLabel,Click poster to enlarge\npaperButtonLabel,Paper / Report\ndashboardButtonLabel,Dashboard\nposterButtonLabel,Poster\nslidesButtonLabel,Prelim Slides\ngithubButtonLabel,GitHub\nwebsiteButtonLabel,Website\naskSagnikButtonLabel,Ask SagnikGPT\nskillsEyebrow,Skills\nskillsTitle,Skills with Evidence\nskillsLead,\"Each skill block is connected to project, coursework, or experience evidence. Click any skill to ask SagnikGPT for a recruiter-style explanation.\"\nskillsAskLabel,Ask skill summary\nskillsAskPrompt,\"Summarize Sagnik's strongest skills with evidence from projects, coursework, research experience, and metrics.\"\nskillAreaHeader,Skill Area\nskillEvidenceHeader,Project Evidence\nskillMethodsHeader,Methods / Tools\nskillActionHeader,Action\nskillEvidenceButtonLabel,Ask evidence ->\nskillCardAskLabel,Ask SagnikGPT for evidence ->\n",
